    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Design of paper structures and mechanisms, such as pop-up elements in books and greeting cards, cut-and-assemble paper models, and various types of paper containers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
